WHEREAS, at the time of his death in 1991, Dr. Aurbach had an
                    international reputation as an endocrinologist, a gifted researcher, an
                    inspiring teacher and a compassionate physician;

RESOLVED that the architectural design guidelines, dated September 17, 2002, and prepared by the Architect for the
                    University, for the Health Sciences Center Parking Structure, are approved;
                    and

